test = {'id': 'null', 'firstName': 'Lelouch', 'lastName': 'Lamperouge',
    'countryOrigin': 'FR', 'countryOriginAlt': 'GB', 'score':

tester = namsorclient.OriginResponse(test)
assert tester.ID == test['id']
